  <lyrics>[V1]
 Munat Tatitojja,
 Ch'amamay churita
 Wawanacamaru
 Parlaña jjataqui.
 
[C]
 Cristo Tatitojjaw
 Nayar khespiyasitu.
 Jiwancamaw arca
 Take chuymajjampi. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Cusisitaw sará
 Alajjpach marcaru.
 Jupaquiw irpitan
 Munasiñapampi.
 
[V3]
 Machak k'ochunaca
 Yatichasitaya,
 Take chuymajjampi
 Yupaychañajjatac.
 
[V4]
 Kollan Ajayuma
 Chuymajjar qhitanim,
 Llaquit chuymajjaru
 Cusisiyañatac.
 
 </lyrics></song>